Welcome Noard
Entrée Selections
To Start
On Transcontinental Flights, We Offer a Selection
of Hors d'Oeuvre at Cocktail Time.
Salads
ON FLIGHTS WEST, We Feature Lasagna Caesar Salad
with Romaine, Lasagna Noodles and Grated Parmesan
Cheese... Oil and Vinegar Dressing.
ON EASTBOUND FLIGHTS, Salade Francaise with
Crisp Greens and an Array of Fresh Vegetables.
Creamy French Dressing.
Desserts
INTERNATIONAL CHEESE AND CRACKERS
FROM THE PATISSERIE
FOR WESTWARD TRAVELERS, We Present Our Swiss
Tart with Vanilla Mousse, Fruit Tidbits, and a Hint of
Kirsch Nested in a Graham Cracker Crust.
ON EASTBOUND FLIGHTS, Enjoy Our
Viennese Plum Cake.
BEEF BOURGUIGNON
Choice Beef Tidbits Simmered in a Hearty Stock with
Burgundy Wine, Onions, Mushrooms and Carrots.
Parslied Potatoes and Peas with Pimentos.
ZARZUELA DE MARISCOS
Fillet of Sole, Scallops and Shrimp in a Golden Egg Sauce with
Almonds. Rice Valencia and Green Beans with Mushrooms.
Trans World Specialties
We have the Enviable Opportunity to Discover Cuisines
from Around the World, and You Are Invited to Share
ONE of Our All Time Favorites.
Your Flight Attendant Will Advise you
WHICH ONE of the Following Has Been Selected Today.
CHICKEN SATE
Chunks of Chicken Breast Coated with Indonesian Spices,
Grilled on a skewer and Presented with a Savory Peanut
Sauce. Curried Rice and Green Beans Cooked in Coconut Juice.
CHEESE FONDUE CASSEROLE
Gruyere and Cheddar Cheese Blended with White Wine
and Brandy, Presented Casserole Style with Smoked
Ham Strips, Toasted Bread Cubes and Broccoli Amandine.
CHICKEN PARMIGIANA
Baked Chicken Breast with a Tangy Tomato Sauce and
COFFEE FLAVORS OF THE WORLD at $1.50 Each
Parmesan Cheese. Italian Vegetable Medley and
The Perfect Touch of Hot Coffee and Whipped
Herb Buttered Spiral Pasta.
Cream, It's the Spirit that Makes the Difference!
BAVARIAN SAUERBRATEN
Jamaican with Kahlua
Royale with Cognac
Marinated Beef Slices Braised in a Slightly Tart Brown
Roma with Galliano
Sauce with Raisins and Apple. Potato Cakes and Red Cabbage.
Please accept our apologies if your choice is not available on today's flight.
